entries.femaleVariant: Where do we get all these parts from anyway? Not like you order 'em.
Oh yeah? And what about all those cars that come out here?
Well, I... I thought you was fixin' 'em.
Hm, better get your eyes checked, son. You never noticed how none of them ever leave?
So all those cars that disappear in Night City...
Reappear in the Badlands. In nature, nothing is lost.
Really? And the NCPD don't do a thing?
What could they do? Their jurisdiction ends at the city line.
